1006c006-e825-4eff-a238-e42dd70b8154	CorteQS için kullanıcıya dönük RAG veritabanı dokümantasyonu (12/13)	| Sorun | Muhtemel neden | Ne kontrol edilmeli |\n|---|---|---|\n| Arama hiç çalışmıyor | `LOVABLE_API_KEY` yok | Edge Function secret / env kontrolü.  |\n| Arama `429` veriyor | Hız limiti | Bir süre bekleyip tekrar deneyin.  |\n| Arama `402` veriyor | Kredi yetersiz | AI sağlayıcı kredisi / workspace kredisi kontrolü.   |\n| Giriş/işlev çağrıları hatalı | Supabase anahtar adı uyuşmuyor | `VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` ile `VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY` eşleştirilmeli.   |\n| WhatsApp bot DB’ye yazmıyor | `SUPABASE_URL` / anahtar eksik | Bot, eksik env’de yazmayı kapatıyor.  |\n| WhatsApp mesajı gitmiyor | `ACCESS_TOKEN` veya `PHONE_NUMBER_ID` sorunu | Meta token geçerliliği ve izinler kontrol edilmeli.  |\n| Realtime çalışmıyor | yayın/izin sorunu | Tablo `supabase_realtime` publication’a ekli mi; erişim anahtarı yetkili mi?     |\n| Dosya geri yüklemede eksik | Sadece DB restore yapıldı | Storage içeriği ayrıca korunmalı; DB backup gerçek obje dosyalarını kapsamaz.   |\n\nBakım görevleri için kullanıcıya dönük ama gerçekçi bir not seti de eklenmelidir. Rollerde değişiklik olduğunda onboarding metinleri ile `user_roles` enum’ları birlikte güncellenmelidir. Yeni kullanıcı modülü eklendiğinde RLS politikası, bildirim trigger’ı ve gerekiyorsa Realtime publication kaydı da beraber tasarlanmalıdır. `referans/` klasörü ile canlı `src/` ve `supabase/migrations` dizinleri arasında senkron kuralı repo içinde açıkça yazıldığı için, bakım ekibi bu farkı düzenli kontrol etmelidir. Ayrıca statik `mock.ts` verisinin canlı veri modeline ne zaman ve nasıl taşınacağı ürün yol haritasının en kritik bakım konularından biridir. Son olarak, şema değiştikçe `src/integrations/supabase/types.ts` dosyasının güncel tutulması gerekir; aksi halde istemci ve DB alanları ayrışır.\n\n## Açık sorular ve varsayımlar\n\nBu çalışmada kesin olarak belirlenemeyen konular aşağıdadır. Kullanıcıya sunulacak nihai dokümantasyonda bunlar gizlenmemeli, doğrudan “belirtilmemiş” olarak işaretlenmelidir.	rag_database_v1.md	{"file": "rag_database_v1.md", "type": "seed", "section": "CorteQS için kullanıcıya dönük RAG veritabanı dokümantasyonu"}	[-0.03692656,-0.0074468562,0.007742448,-0.05775824,-0.005838493,0.0012861099,-0.011155983,0.0029491698,-0.01311773,-0.009973642,-0.014622065,0.016779585,0.018152228,0.02444817,0.13803262,-0.007023561,0.020257885,0.029189605,0.0012799586,0.020199545,0.02604275,0.008416795,0.018259874,-0.007775681,-0.015709076,0.009571527,0.036588125,-0.006155885,0.0073063527,0.0006740233,-0.001199848,0.0033368126,0.0040031536,0.037310902,-0.009350265,0.027753297,0.004360997,0.0013672896,0.0011631341,0.03333169,0.024217656,0.003661138,0.027183844,-0.0042517968,-0.010698067,0.016768327,-0.021133201,-0.031846777,-0.00877883,0.02022058,0.010119341,0.000472946,0.0011232728,-0.17111471,0.0062624584,-0.02238507,-0.041976817,0.01020509,0.016269056,-0.017313577,-0.015869908,0.0449745,-0.020276213,-0.006531808,-0.009837126,0.013248043,0.02583783,0.0011355624,0.00304969,-0.015683994,-0.015399411,-0.020750614,-0.015336996,-0.022784444,-0.010830238,-0.015043816,0.0076457923,0.002177814,0.003748796,-0.004513985,-0.02874098,-0.01120272,-0.011412869,-0.007620636,0.012827489,-0.0038172777,0.026140276,0.012004507,0.00032874788,0.011215371,0.009264136,0.016782284,0.014220949,-0.016655533,-0.004034756,0.017589828,0.008866957,0.019798238,0.017902574,-0.017995223,-0.014588782,3.5829904e-05,0.02260292,0.02793988,0.008266838,0.014431164,0.0153436465,-0.0072782123,-0.008943032,0.008067208,0.013901256,-0.015230302,0.011380419,-0.022127185,-0.01975954,-0.16308431,0.0030970797,-0.016063446,-0.0015850998,0.01966446,-0.02456901,0.019683644,0.01675442,-0.0022119614,-0.017532807,-0.020103263,0.01246358,-0.006524967,0.0076899454,-0.0034863523,-0.026652347,0.0033274947,-0.0027642013,-0.010758108,-0.01401177,0.02492526,0.005632474,0.015847346,-0.016669247,-0.008802162,0.004734907,0.01